Bugs:
Next/Prev does nothing when nothing was played yet.
Seekbar gets stuck at start (Reproduce by playing last part of T-ara - I go crazy because of you. At the end of song seekbar gets stuck).
At exit last.fm doesnt scrobble currently playing track if it's the case.

Features:
Save playlists.
Save current playlist + current position.
Save volume.
Save cursor follows playback.
click status to go to current song in playlist.
Random track.
Plugins.
Splits - album artist.
Multiple cds.
Cue sheets.
ctrl+j focus filter box